{"tid":892452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秀茂坪邨單位閉門失火　逾百居民逃生　一老翁扭傷腳送院","createTime":"2018-11-07T01:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T02:49:54.000Z","uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"997c7fb310441f7a9fd0dd7f47c57e40afc7637f","tid":892452,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"2018-11-07 06:25<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-11-07 06:41<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/255968/%E7%A7%80%E8%8C%82%E5%9D%AA%E9%82%A8%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E9%96%89%E9%96%80%E5%A4%B1%E7%81%AB-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E9%80%83%E7%94%9F-%E4%B8%80%E8%80%81%E7%BF%81%E6%89%AD%E5%82%B7%E8%85%B3%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F255968%2F%25E7%25A7%2580%25E8%258C%2582%25E5%259D%25AA%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E9%2596%2589%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%25BF%2581%25E6%2589%25AD%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2585%25B3%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2&d=3tFsguQ86tV6gLW7RkUBTzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2e96d58a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/255968/%E7%A7%80%E8%8C%82%E5%9D%AA%E9%82%A8%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E9%96%89%E9%96%80%E5%A4%B1%E7%81%AB-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E9%80%83%E7%94%9F-%E4%B8%80%E8%80%81%E7%BF%81%E6%89%AD%E5%82%B7%E8%85%B3%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2062520/org/233e45fc7d57002f0ddfe0919cc067c9.jpg/miVuUV5gdjALBQVXGWti-9iuvOtFyNpKR4afW22Gn1s?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2062520%2Forg%2F233e45fc7d57002f0ddfe0919cc067c9.jpg%2FmiVuUV5gdjALBQVXGWti-9iuvOtFyNpKR4afW22Gn1s%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=3a26718f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周三（7日）清晨約5時26分，秀茂坪邨秀緻樓一高層單位突然起火，大批居民漏夜逃生及報警求助，逾150人疏散到安全地方，惟其中一名老翁逃生期間扭傷腳部，在親友陪同下由救護員送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n消防接報趕抵動用一條喉及一隊煙帽隊灌救，約半小時後將火救熄。消息稱，起火單位位於30樓，火警時單位內並沒有人，消防現正調查起火原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想同呢條女瘋狂逃生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e142b0dc040279e1bbb3d26c78e796e1939c91ca","tid":892452,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd448359501a66e84a1822b4fbaf14bfa16fc31f","tid":892452,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"點解好似日日有屋村火燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9bdd1d17f5717616e47d476e530b8c7ece6069","tid":892452,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:17:34.000Z","msg":"幾正"},{"pid":"6148d215956a7c4a7141876ebe52a916ab448f4e","tid":892452,"uid":48150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/07/102350_46c599c1c522f46717330b054f26bd53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F07%2F102350_46c599c1c522f46717330b054f26bd53.png&h=1e040e37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee4a6730655c327f18f04069658c07dc3a80018d","tid":892452,"uid":90499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"法官大人!"}]}